                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280110-175-off918 t18280110-175-crimeloc921"></join>. Between one and two o'clock on the 10th of January I saw the prisoner come and put his arm, and half his body, into my shop; I ran out of my room, and pursued<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182801100093"></xptr>him: I found him in my father's custody, with these boots, which are my property.</p>
